Description: Read, explore and visualize camera trap data following the
    Camtrap DP (Camera Trap Data Package, <https://camtrap-dp.tdwg.org/>)
    data exchange format. With camtraptor you can read and filter data,
    get summaries of observed species and deployment information, and
    visualize these summaries on an interactive map.
